revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}
{{Template shortcut|fla}}
==Usage==
:<code>{{{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|</nowiki>''Athlete's name''|''Country code or name''|''optional flag variant''|code=''optional code value''}}</code>

==Examples==
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Michael Phelps]]|USA}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Bjørn Dæhlie]]|NOR}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Nedo Nadi]]|ITA|1861}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Elisabeta Lipă]]|ROU|1965}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Daley Thompson]]|ENG}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Daley Thompson]]|GBR}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Werner Günthör]]|SUI}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Orukpe Erayokan]]|NIG}}</nowiki>}}
{{nowiki template demo|format=inline|output=nowiki+|code=<nowiki>{{</nowiki>{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|[[Jasna Šekarić]]|FR Yugoslavia|code=YUG}}</nowiki>}}

==Parameters==
{{TemplateDataHeader}}
<templatedata>
{
	"params": {
		"1": {
			"label": "Athlete's name",
			"description": "Name of the athlete. May be wikilinked.",
			"type": "content",
			"required": true
		},
		"2": {
			"label": "Country code or name",
			"description": "Selects the country whose flag is to be shown.",
			"example": "ITA",
			"type": "string",
			"required": true
		},
		"3": {
			"aliases": [
				"variant"
			],
			"label": "Variant",
			"description": "Selects the variant of the flag to be used; see Template:Flag.",
			"example": "1965",
			"type": "string"
		},
		"code": {
			"label": "Country code for display",
			"description": "The code to display after the name, if different to parameter 2, \"Country code or name\".",
			"example": "YUG",
			"default": "The value of parameter 2."
		}
	},
	"description": "Generates an inline flag, followed by an athlete's name, followed by a country code.",
	"format": "inline"
}
</templatedata>


==Alternatives to avoid Wikipedia's [[WP:PEIS|Post-expand include size]] limit==
Pages with many flag icons may come close to or exceed Wikipedia's [[WP:PEIS|Post-expand include size]] limit.  In these cases consider using modules or module-wrapper templates instead:
* {{tl|flagg}} is a simple wrapper for [[Module:Flagg]]: For basic use, <code>{{{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|</nowiki>''athlete's name''<nowiki>|</nowiki>''country code or name''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code> can be replaced with <code><nowiki>{{flagg|unaep|</nowiki>''country code or name''<nowiki>|</nowiki>preftext=''athlete's name''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>. To use IOC country codes, replace <code>unaep</code> with <code>unaepi</code>.
* {{ml|flag|athlete}} is a wrapper for [[Module:Flagg]] that can further reduce sizes when invoked directly. For basic use, <code>{{{{BASEPAGENAME}}<nowiki>|</nowiki>''athlete's name''<nowiki>|</nowiki>''country code or name''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code> can be replaced with <code><nowiki>{{#invoke:flag|athlete|</nowiki>''athlete's name''<nowiki>|</nowiki>''country code or name''<nowiki>}}</nowiki></code>.  To use IOC country codes, add {{para|opts|i}}.

==See also==
*[[Template:Flag team]], a similar template useful for entire teams instead of individual names
*[[Template:Flag medalist]] a similar template with expanded country names
*[[Template:Flag link medalist]] a similar template with expanded country names and country info on one line
*[[Template:Flag]] and [[Template:Flag icon]] for additional discussion about flag variations
*[[Template:Flag IOC athlete]], a similar template for use with athletes at the Olympics
*[[Template:Flag link athlete]], a similar template to provide links to countries at editions of athletics championships

{{Flag templates}}

<includeonly>{{sandbox other||
<!-- Categories below this line and interwikis at Wikidata -->
[[Category:Flag template system]]
}}</includeonly>

